{"tid":1869201,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[星期六日唔收貨] 網購口罩集運討論7","createTime":"2020-02-08T05:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T07:11:00.000Z","uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"48976142d945a3e0194e31228cd8c007b2f10606","tid":1869201,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:03:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>內容及資料僅供參考，投資涉及風險，口罩價格可升亦可跌，甚至變成亳無價值。投資者在決定是否購買有關口罩之前應先閱讀有關風險評估，以了解該建議發售之詳細資料，並應就本身的財務、其他狀況及需要，詳細考慮並決定購買有關口罩是否切合本身特定的需要，若有需要更應咨詢其他專業意見，方可作出有關購買決定。<br />\n忠告：親自買罩 咪俾錢炒狗</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n間間集運都爆，唔好再問邊間快啲邊間好用，根本就無人知。記得留意返集運公司對體積重收費同要求，隨時運費貴過口罩本身，重有拒收嘅風險存在。<br />\nTENSO寄DHL要另外查詢寄電郵，佢要另外再同你度貨物SIZE計運費。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>日本快遞公司代號</strong><br />\nAmazon自己送<br />\nカトーレック= Katolec = 老人<br />\nヤマト運輸 = Yamato = 貓<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>麻煩大家Amazon唔好再用殘體字 有得揀英文/日文</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zsq6yyZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzsq6yyZ.jpg&h=8752b55a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6bac9a3e0a05eb35a2e602f4dc3e0744e666de1","tid":1869201,"uid":29186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad113fcc82caf88dbc3475507bac45f90031172","tid":1869201,"uid":29912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T06:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa